55128::$$$message_0488_0000_0000$$$::   I'm the only one who can move easily.[lr]::
55129::$$$message_0488_0000_0001$$$::Both Archer and Tohsaka have been disabled by Rider's Mystic Eyes.[lr]::
55130::$$$message_0488_0000_0002$$$::So, if we remove the common cause...!::
55131::$$$message_0488_0001_0000$$$::I run at Rider.[lr]::
55132::$$$message_0488_0001_0001$$$::Even if I can't take her down, I can at least break her gaze on Archer for a second!::
55133::$$$message_0488_0001_0002$$$::"...!? Have you lost your mind!? Don't look directly at Rider!"[lr]::
55134::$$$message_0488_0001_0003$$$::I ignore Archer's voice and charge at Rider.::
55135::$$$message_0488_0001_0004$$$::   If those Mystic Eyes petrify people, then I can just close my eyes.[lr]::
55136::$$$message_0488_0001_0005$$$::The hallway is narrow.[lr]::
55137::$$$message_0488_0001_0006$$$::I know how far I am from Rider.[lr]::
55138::$$$message_0488_0001_0007$$$::Whether Rider reacts to me or I manage to pull off my suicide charge, it might create an opening for Archer...!::
55139::$$$message_0488_0001_0008$$$::   But, my legs are frozen.[lr]::
55140::$$$message_0488_0001_0009$$$::   They've actually turned to stone.::
55141::$$$message_0488_0002_0000$$$::"Wha..."[lr]::
55142::$$$message_0488_0002_0001$$$::Not just my legs.[lr]::
55143::$$$message_0488_0002_0002$$$::The petrification reaches my waist, hardening my torso, freezing my arms, and sealing my eyelids shut forever.[lr]::
55144::$$$message_0488_0002_0003$$$::"Ev...?"::
55145::$$$message_0488_0003_0000$$$::"How foolish.[lr]::
55146::$$$message_0488_0003_0001$$$::Did you think closing your eyes would be enough to block my Mystic Eyes? Everything I see is cursed, whether physical or spiritual."::
55147::$$$message_0488_0004_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
55148::$$$message_0488_0004_0001$$$::My throat and mouth won't move.[lr]::
55149::$$$message_0488_0004_0002$$$::...I can't even tell what's happening around me.[lr]::
55150::$$$message_0488_0004_0003$$$::I'm a stone statue that has no way of knowing[lr]::
55151::$$$message_0488_0004_0004$$$::whether Tohsaka's screaming,[lr]::
55152::$$$message_0488_0004_0005$$$::or Archer's crumbling to pieces.::
55153::$$$message_0488_0005_0000$$$::My body is stone, and soon, my mind will follow.[lr]::
55154::$$$message_0488_0005_0001$$$::...In ancient myth, there were three immortal sisters.[lr]::
55155::$$$message_0488_0005_0002$$$::Just like them, my body will never change.:ù#g